        dc:description           "Figure 29. (a–e) Hapalotremus marcapata sp. nov., female holotype (MUBI). (a) Labium, ventral view. (b) Eyes, dorsal view. (c) Tarsus IV, ventral view. (d) Tarsus IV, prolateral view. (e) Spermathecae, dorsal view. Scale bar: 1 mm. Photos: Nelson Ferretti." ;
